import Filters from './Filters'
import Filter from './Filter'
import SelectOptions from '../SelectOptions'
import Loader from '../Loader'


const SubpageContent = props => {
  switch (props.content) {
    case "filters":
      return <Filters show={props.show}/>
    case "clientTypeFilter":
      return <SelectOptions selected={props.activeFilter} options={props.options} filter={props.filter} onChange={props.onChange} type="radio"/>
    case "clientTypeFilter..":
      return <Filter filter="clientTypes" label="Client Type" activeFilter={props.activeFilters.clientTypes} options={props.catalogue.clientTypes} onChange={props.onChange}  type="radio" />
    default:
      return <Loader />
  }

}

export default SubpageContent
